Define specific Compas attributes to identify uniquely one IED with-in a SystemVersion for a given ICD, IEDredundancy, IEDSystemVersionInstance The IEDType defines the set of LD which are supported by the hardware The VendorName, IEDmodel, hwRev, swRev, headerId, headerVersion, headerRevision are issued from the ICD file The UUID of this combination is defined by the ICDSystemVersionUUID. This private is intended to be used in the STD file (/IED level) and SSD (/LNode level) At LNode level it defines the link between the Function, the associated LD, LN and the implementation in a given IED At IED level, it defines the link of the IED within the SystemVersion
